Sydney Lewis

Bio

Hi! Im a graduate student at Johns Hopkins Bloomberg School of Public Health and Im studying epidemiology with a focus on pharmacoepidemiology. Im excited for future opportunities to learn more about drug development, safety, and utilization.

Outside of school, I love to run , sew , and cook . Im originally from Southern California and Im having so much fun exploring Baltimore!
